---
title: Plant-Based Ravioli & Creamy Mushroom Sauce with Balsamic Rocket
description: Let’s veggie-fy this plant-based ravioli packed full of pumpkin and coated in a creamy sauce cooked with hearty mushrooms. Add a zap of freshness with a peppery rocket to finish with a punch of flavour.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
